quote-text: Lily, this year, this nasty, schoolyard-bully of a year, will not stop punching me in the face. How did we kick off two thousand and eleven? My dad died.  And now, after five months of unemployment,  I just blew my dream job. Good news is, in a few seconds, I’m going to start heaving my guts out because, that’s what life is for me now. Just loosing what’s inside until I’m just empty.
quote-source: Jason Segel as Marshall Eriksen, How I Met Your Mother S6E24 “Challenge Accepted”
